column7: How satisfied are you with life as a whole these days? (ql4c1ak)
column8: How enjoyable is your life as a whole these days? (dzyh760)
column47: Imagine I gave you a "REPLAY YESTERDAY" button. When pressed, this button would cause you to be instantly transported back in time to yesterday morning. You would live the day again exactly the same as you did the first time. You would have no recollection of pressing the button. *Would you press this button to replay yesterday?* (6jkjlca)
column49: Imagine I gave you a "SKIP TOMORROW" button. When pressed, this button would cause you to be instantly transported 24 hours into the future. You still do all the things you would normally do (so nobody else can tell any difference), and remember the day normally, you just don't experience it. Afterwards, you forget you pressed the button. *Would you press this button to skip tomorrow?* (5jpyee3)
